{
  "stem": "22047.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "If we-- an attack was pending, we'd go out and assume these foxholes that we'd dug.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And one day, pretty traumatic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "I was out there with my platoon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And one of the sergeants in our company was supervising the digging of these holes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And he was hit almost point blank by an 88 artillery round.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "Ooh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Sort of messed him up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And so we spent a good deal of time in that area, until it was determined that we were out on a-- on quite a salient.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "So we had to pull back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And this one-- one night, we pulled back and it was snowing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And the roads were icy and we had half-tracks and trucks slipping off the road.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And we had to pull back about 25 miles to solidify the line.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't have too many.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a few captured.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The night we moved back from-- from this outpost, we-- I had three, four of the men in my company were captured.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They got-- wandered off somewhere and got captured.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't have any-- any wounded on the outpost.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "During the patrols that were sent out, we lost probably a dozen out of our whole company.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't lose any people from my platoon during that period of time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Our job was-- was on a defensive position.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We did a lot of patrolling, contact patrols with the unit-- units on either side, and would look for German patrols and what they were doing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So it was mostly patrolling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't-- and on one of these patrols, we had a-- a number of folks from another platoon killed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In fact, one of the guys that I was quite friendly with who was a platoon leader was killed on one night.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
